The minister promised to reduce the country's dependence on
fish imports and work towards stimulating local fish production
through favorable government policies on fisheries and allied
products.
</P>
<P>
"Through you and through our departments of fisheries of the
ministry, if we are able to galvanize our fishermen as well as our
fish farmers, within a space of time, we can reduce substantially
the importation," he said.
</P>
<P>
"And gradually, overtime, given the commitment, we can even
stop importing fish," he added. 
