<HEADLINE> Xinhua Photo List for April 12 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 12 (Xinhua) -- Following is the photo list for
April 12 released by Xinhua:
</P>
<P>
1. Chinese President Jiang Zemin leaves Beijing for five-nation
visit.
</P>
<P>
2. Visiting Chinese Vice-Premier Li Lanqing holds talk with
Cuban Vice-President Carlos Lage Davila.
</P>
<P>
3. Cuban President Fidel Castro meets visiting Chinese Vice-
Premier Li Lanqing.
</P>
<P>
4. Visiting Chinese Vice-Premier Li Lanqing meets President of
Madagascar Didier Ratsirak.
</P>
<P>
5. Chinese Vice-President Hu Jintao meets Madagascar guest.
</P>
<P>
6. CEO of American Tupperware Company receives "Marco Polo
Award" in Beijing.
</P>
