<TEXT>
<P>
GENEVA, April 12 (Xinhua) -- European soccer's governing body
has delayed a decision on whether Turkey's Galatasaray fans will
be allowed to attend the second leg of the UEFA Cup semi-final
against Leeds United of England until Friday.
</P>
