part of the Torch Program, a plan launched in 1988 for the
commercial and industrial use of scientific developments and the
promotion of high technology industries.
</P>
<P>
NEU-Alpine, established in conjunction with Northeast
University's (NEU) software center, operates more than 30 Chinese
subsidiaries engaged in software development and marketing.
