foreign exchange earnings from the overseas recruitment of
Indonesian manpower in the past five years have reached 1.9
billion U.S dollars in the Asia Pacific region, 1.5 billion
dollars in the Middle East, 80.8 million dollars in America and 32.
04 million dollars in Europe. 
